    "Translations of the dataset in other languages can be used, either from English to the target language or by leveraging the already translated Spanish dataset to obtain another in a close (Romance) language.",
    "The proposed method in this research is applicable to larger Language Model architectures (LLMs) and is compatible with current quantization and training enhancement techniques.",
    "This approach is portable to other languages, provided any modern MT system has support for it.",
    "Incorporating an EWC into the training process to prevent catastrophic forgetting and increasing the learning of new weights in the NER system is another potential future project.",
